cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "2D Physics-Informed Neural Network for Glomerular Filtration"
version: "1.1.0"
date-released: "2025-05-18"
doi: "10.5281/zenodo.19892890"
license: MIT
repository-code: "https://github.com/baysquire/pinn-glomerular-filtration"
url: "https://github.com/baysquire/pinn-glomerular-filtration"
abstract: >
  A 2D Physics-Informed Neural Network (PINN) for simulating solute transport
  in a simplified glomerular capillary under normotensive and hypertensive
  conditions. Embeds a Poiseuille-convection-diffusion-reaction PDE into the
  network loss function. Validated against the analytical solution of the
  1D steady-state convection-diffusion equation (L2 error: 2.64e-4).
authors:
